== Horudhac ==

Sistamka Isgaarsiinta Caalamaka ee teleefonada gacanta oo loo soo gaabiyo GSM (Global System for Mobile Communication) waa farsamo iyo shuruuc la'dejiyay taasoo sababtay in telefoonada gacanta ee caalamka ee isu soo dhawaadaan oo ay sahlaan in horumarintooda lagawada qaybqaato.

Magaca GSM waa magac loo bixiyey koox dhisay sanadka markii uu ahaa 1982 looguna talagalay in ay sameeyo shuruuc (standard) midaysan kaas oo dhoqda mid wada mideeya dhamaan isgaarsiinta teleefonada gacanta qaarada [[yurub]]. Sistamkaasna waxaa loo qorsheeyay in uu ku shakheeyo hirarka 900 MHz.  GSM is the name of a standardization group established in 1982 to create a common European mobile telephone standard that would formulate specifications for a pan-European mobile cellular radio system operating at 900 MHz. It is estimated that many countries outside of Europe will join the GSM partnership.


